          />
          in/anandubabukr</a
        >
      </li>
    </ul>
  </div>

  <footer class="flex pt-4 my-8 -t">
    <a class="mx-auto font-bold tracking-wider text-orange-400" href="/"
      >Portfolio</a
    >
  </footer>
</ResumeLayout>
